      <p>Heals:</p>
      1
    </div>
    <div class="group__dps column has-text-centered">
      <p>DPS:</p>
      2
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="group__description column has-text-centered">
    Looking for a group to get into deadmines! Tank/Healer LF2M Dps. Looking to do
    full run!
  </div>
</div>

